messages.message: Also, when I do load a large file (44mb) successfully the UI is failing with Error loading image : Unable to display image '/api/v2/files/dale.deloy/my-repo/fs/Instabase Drive/aihub/44dd9711-7081-422b-b371-3a5f4492642e/documents/out/original/images/Redacted Med Records Example <#C05LLRV7VK3|> - first half_29da22ec5af728e3469ed840f800cf00c31344afeffc842170db92363669f487.pdf_p0.JPEG.jpeg?expect-node-type=file'

I think I found the issue here: the file name had the # symbol within it.  Removing that symbol fixed the error.  Suggest looking at removing symbols that are allowed in file names that create errors.
